pmn01a-data-displayed-survey: Idatha eboniswe kule dashboard iqokelelwa ngokuthe ngqo kwiimpendulo zesaveyi kwaye ayiveli kwizibalo zelizwe elisemthethweni okanye iiseti zedatha. Imele izimvo ezivakaliswe ngabantu abatsha ngexesha lophando, kwaye naziphi na izigqibo ezithathwe kwezi mpendulo zixanduva lomsebenzisi, kungekhona i-PMNCH. I-PMNCH izibophelele ekuhlonipheni, ekukhuthazeni nasekukhuseleni amalungelo kunye nokuphila kakuhle kwabo bonke abantu. Naziphi na iimbono ezivakaliswe kwiimpendulo zesaveyi okanye izinto ezipapashiweyo ezivela kule dashboard eziphikisana nesi sibophelelo azixhaswa yi-PMNCH.
